  "id": "RAW_f93f5578",
  "title": "打破确定性魔咒！北航团队提出 VBF++：用“不确定性建模”刷新多模态视频推荐 SOTA",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247651249&idx=2&sn=ed151c2b07680a2225b537bace935550",
  "date": "2025-12-15 06:52:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"145\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100167546\" data-ratio=\"0.2515625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=990cc1ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnqHORUE28eAnPBy2YsmzFhoKbqECbicfDkWHUF9JxicBIUlDSm42IKq8ZONibnLIGvQyKEsL4xAtVMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | 刘瑞 </span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">审校 | 蔡芳芳</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">论文题目</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">： VBF++: Variational Bayesian Fusion with Context-Aware Priors and Recommendation-Guided Adversarial Refinement for Multimodal Video Recommendation</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">作者单位</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">： 北京航空航天大学 &amp; 北京邮电大学</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">参考代码</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">： <a href=\"https://github.com/muhhpu/VBF\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/muhhpu/VBF</a></span></span></p>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n       <p><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">痛点：确定性融合的</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;color: #4285f4;caret-color: red;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">“不确定性”危机</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">多模态视频推荐系统在捕捉用户兴趣时，需要高效整合视频的视觉、听觉和文本特征。然而，现有的主流方法（如基于注意力机制或图神经网络的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">确定性融合</span>方法 [2-3]）面临着一个根本性的挑战：它们倾向于为给定的输入计算一个单一的、最优的权重向量，将多模态融合视为寻找“全局唯一最优解”的优化问题 。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种“点估计”的策略，在面对真实世界短视频生态中的三大“不确定性”时 [5-6]，显得尤为脆弱 ：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">认知不确定性 (Epistemic Uncertainty)</span>： 面对噪声干扰、模态缺失或语义模糊的短视频内容时，单一的融合方案往往不够鲁棒，忽略了可能存在的多个合理的融合策略空间 。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">上下文无关的简单先验</span>： 现有的变分方法虽然引入了概率建模，但通常假设视频内容服从相同的简单分布（如标准高斯分布 ）[4]，忽略了不同语义类别（如动作片对视觉的依赖 vs. 音乐片对听觉的依赖）对模态依赖的结构化差异 。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">目标错位 (Objective Misalignment)</span>： 传统变分自编码器（VAE）优化的证据下界（ELBO）目标主要关注特征重构质量，而推荐系统追求的是排序准确性（Ranking）。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">重构得好不等于推荐得准</span>&nbsp;。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n       <p><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">范式革新：VBF++ 将融合从</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);caret-color: red;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">“点估计”升级为“分布建模”</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-size:16px;line-height:27px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">近日，北京航空航天大学和北京邮电大学联合提出了一种全新的概率化框架—VBF++（Variational Bayesian Fusion with Context-Aware Priors and Recommendation-Guided Adversarial Refinement）</span><sup><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></sup><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">VBF++ 的核心思想是将多模态融合过程重新表述为一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">变分推理问题</span>，成功将融合范式从传统的“点估计”转变为更具鲁棒性的“分布建模”范式。</span></p>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-size:16px;line-height:27px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">该框架认为：每个视频&nbsp;</span><em><span leaf=\"\">V</span><sub><span leaf=\"\">i</span></sub></em><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;关联一个潜在的随机融合策略变量&nbsp;</span><em><span leaf=\"\">Z</span><sub><span leaf=\"\">i</span></sub></em><span leaf=\"\">，通过捕捉&nbsp;</span><em><span leaf=\"\">Z</span><sub><span leaf=\"\">i&nbsp;</span></sub></em><span leaf=\"\">的随机性，模型能够量化融合权重的可信度，保留多种可能的融合解释。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">VBF++ 的整体框架（图 1）由三大关键组件构成，完美解决了上述挑战：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">上下文感知的结构化先验 (Context-Aware Prior)；</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐引导的对抗性优化 (Recommendation-Guided Adversarial Refinement, RAR)；</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于元学习的域适应 (Meta-Learner)。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100167562\" data-ratio=\"0.55390625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7d3301b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnqHORUE28eAnPBy2YsmzFhCR4dMiab9PukHtiakXeBk2fFrxwpuqc7una0IABapYVFY9sicQU7tx2pw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图 1 VBF++ 的分层概率模型框架。包含上下文感知先验、变分后验、动态融合网络及对抗优化模块。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">VBF++ 三大核心创新点深度解析</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;height: 52px;line-height: 61px;color: #4285f4;font-weight: 500;background: none no-repeat left center;background-size: 45px auto;padding-left: 30px;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">结构化先验：让模型“见微知著”</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了解决简单高斯先验的局限性，VBF++ 设计了一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">可学习的混合先验机制</span>。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不是简单地假设所有视频都一样，而是根据视频的语义类别（如动作片、</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">音乐片、纪录片等），动态调整融合策略的先验分布。模型将视频划分为</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:8px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:8px;line-height:1.8em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">个语义簇，并为每个簇学习特定的先验分布中心</span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167564\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4634760705289673\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1191\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee203923&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnqHORUE28eAnPBy2YsmzFhcNtjBBAW7jnibFEia3I8FSv27TZDrmibvnicISCa57NsQFJfU0aVfXnUMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图 2 训练前后融合策略的 t-SNE 可视化。训练后策略自动聚类成有意义的语义群组。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">效果验证</span>：训练后的策略在潜在空间中自动聚类成明显的语义群组（见图 2），且这种聚类与视频内容高度一致（见图 3）：</span></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">动作类视频自动赋予视觉模态更高权重（平均 0.68）。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">音乐类视频声学模态权重显著增加（平均 0.71）。</span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">纪录片中文本描述的权重占主导（平均 0.59）。</span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100167582\" data-ratio=\"1.28359375\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ed11a39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnqHORUE28eAnPBy2YsmzFhRUHCHNGM1TticRXwt3j3cBGcmZppibBAkhP60m2vZDeJ0qy0M1kaUMibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n      <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图 3 学习融合策略与后验不确定性分析。(a) 模态权重分布具有语义适应性。(b) 后验不确定性分析表明，内容模糊的视频具有更高的不确定性。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;height: 52px;line-height: 61px;color: #4285f4;font-weight: 500;background: none no-repeat left center;background-size: 45px auto;padding-left: 30px;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">RAR：用对抗学习对齐推荐目标</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是 VBF++ 解决“目标错位”的核心利器。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统的 ELBO 损失侧重重构，VBF++ 引入了 RAR (Recommendation-Guided Adversarial Refinement) 范式：</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">经验回放缓冲区 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ：首先，模型收集那些推荐损失 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;较低的、高质量的融合策略 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">对抗训练：随后，引入一个判别器&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;，通过对抗性训练强制编码器（生成器）生成的融合策略分布</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;逼近这个高质量策略的集合 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">简而言之，RAR 机制显式地将变分学习导向了推荐排序目标，确保了模型在保持多样性的同时，生成的策略是真正“好用”的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;height: 52px;line-height: 61px;color: #4285f4;font-weight: 500;background: none no-repeat left center;background-size: 45px auto;padding-left: 30px;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">元学习：应对冷启动与快速适应</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了适应快速变化的短视频环境和跨域推荐，VBF++ 集成了元学习器（Meta-Learner）。该模块利用 MAML 思想，通过梯度更新快速调整模型参数</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">θ</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，实现<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">对新内容和新领域的快速</span>适应，有效解决了新内容的冷启动问题。</span></p>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n       <p><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;实验结果：刷新 SOTA，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;color: #4285f4;caret-color: red;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">兼顾多样性与准确性</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;height: 52px;line-height: 61px;color: #4285f4;font-weight: 500;background: none no-repeat left center;background-size: 45px auto;padding-left: 30px;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">实验与结果</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">VBF++ 在 MovieLens-10M、TikTok 和 Kuaishou 三个真实世界数据集上进行了全面评估，如表 1。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100167565\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"1\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100167566\" data-ratio=\"0.296875\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fa6d7277&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnqHORUE28eAnPBy2YsmzFhXyjl7UTBWPm5vyFOibQeSorlasvPeUPUff9icV6u915GibzwAPdsTSdkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">表 1 &nbsp;VBF++ 与现有 SOTA 方法在三个数据集上的性能对比</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">全面 SOTA</span>：VBF++ 在所有数据集和指标上均超越了包括 LightGCN、MMGCN、LATTICE 等 14 种现有的基线方法。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">稀疏数据表现</span>：在数据稀疏的 TikTok 数据集上，相比最先进的 MVideoRec，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Precision@10 提升了 4.7% - 8.3%</span>，证明了概率化融合在处理不确定性和噪声方面的有效性。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">跨域适应性</span>：在跨域推荐设置下，VBF++ 相比基线取得了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;18.0% - 25.2%&nbsp;</span>的显著提升，验证了元学习与不确定性建模结合后的强大泛化能力。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;height: 52px;line-height: 61px;color: #4285f4;font-weight: 500;background: none no-repeat left center;background-size: 45px auto;padding-left: 30px;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">策略空间可视化：确定性 vs. 概率性</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">VBF++ 最大的优势在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">于保持推荐准确性的同时，量化了融合策略的可信度</span>。图 4 展示了传统注意力机制与 VBF++ 在对同一视频进行 100 次推理时，其融合策略在潜在空间中的分布差异：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167567\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5748c3a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnqHORUE28eAnPBy2YsmzFhUdBWeASaaJDY6najicml4TPswRjMibj8Ne1Oy94kNI9ESoEVO5NGqKuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图 4 传统注意力机制（左）与 VBF++（右）在同一输入下的融合策略分布对比。颜色梯度表示策略质量。</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">传统注意力（左）</span>：结果几乎<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">坍缩在空间中的同一个点</span>，模型缺乏弹性，无法对融合权重的可信度进行建模。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">VBF++（右）</span>：策略分布呈现出一个结构化的椭圆置信区域，围绕在高质量策略中心附近（绿色 / 黄色点）。这证明模型成功学习到了一个后验分布</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;，在保留必要探索空间的同时，确保了准确性。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251215080710_9c8f29fd&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">总结与展望</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">VBF++ 成功地为多模态视频推荐系统引入了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">不确定性建模</span>，实现了从确定性点估计到变分贝叶斯融合的范式转变。通过三大创新模块——上下文感知先验、推荐引导的对抗优化和元学习，VBF++ 不仅刷新了 SOTA 性能，更生成了具有可解释性和语义意义的融合策略。这项工作为处理多模态数据中的不确定性和噪声提供了坚实的理论基础和有效的解决方案。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考文献</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Cao, Z., Liu, R., &amp; Chen, Y. (2025). VBF++: Variational Bayesian Fusion with Context-Aware Priors and Recommendation-Guided Adversarial Refinement for Multimodal Video Recommendation. Beihang University &amp; BUPT.</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Wei, Y., Wang, X., Nie, L., He, X., Hong, R., &amp; Chua, T. S. (2019). MMGCN: Multi-modal Graph Convolution Network for Personalized Recommendation of Micro-video. Proceedings of the 27th ACM International Conference on Multimedia (MM '19), 1437–1445.</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Zhang, C., et al. (2021). Mining Latent Structures for Multimedia Recommendation. Proceedings of the 29th ACM International Conference on Multimedia (MM '21).</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Liang, D., Krishnan, R. G., Hoffman, M. D., &amp; Jebara, T. (2018). Variational Autoencoders for Collaborative Filtering. Proceedings of the 2018 World Wide Web Conference (WWW '18), 689–698.</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Kingma, D. P., &amp; Welling, M. (2014). Auto-Encoding Variational Bayes. International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR).</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Higgins, I., et al. (2017). beta-VAE: Learning Basic Visual Concepts with a Constrained Variational Framework. International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR).</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "北航团队提出的 VBF++模型通过引入不确定性建模、上下文感知先验和推荐引导的对抗优化，将多模态视频推荐从“点估计”升级为“分布建模”，大幅提升了推荐系统的准确性和鲁棒性，刷新了 SOTA 性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "北航团队提出的 VBF++模型通过引入不确定性建模、上下文感知先验和推荐引导的对抗优化，将多模态视频推荐从“点估计”升级为“分布建模”，大幅提升了推荐系统的准确性和鲁棒性，刷新了 SOTA 性能。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了北京航空航天大学和北京邮电大学联合提出的 VBF++多模态视频推荐模型。该模型针对现有确定性融合方法在处理视频不确定性、简单先验和目标错位问题时的不足，创新性地将多模态融合过程重构为变分推理问题。VBF++通过三大核心组件：上下文感知的结构化先验动态调整模态融合策略，推荐引导的对抗性优化（RAR）将变分学习与推荐排序目标对齐，以及基于元学习的域适应模块解决冷启动问题。实验结果表明，VBF++在 MovieLens-10M、TikTok 和 Kuaishou 等真实数据集上全面超越了现有 SOTA 方法，尤其在稀疏数据和跨域推荐场景下表现出色，验证了其在复杂多模态环境下的有效性和泛化能力。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统多模态视频推荐在面对不确定性时面临挑战。",
      "explanation": "现有的确定性融合方法（如注意力机制或图神经网络）将多模态融合视为寻找“全局唯一最优解”的优化问题，但在面对噪声干扰、模态缺失、语义模糊以及目标错位（重构好不等于推荐准）时，显得尤为脆弱。"
    },
    {
      "point": "VBF++将多模态融合从“点估计”升级为更鲁棒的“分布建模”范式。",
      "explanation": "VBF++的核心思想是将融合过程重新表述为变分推理问题，通过捕捉融合策略的随机性，量化融合权重的可信度，保留多种可能的融合解释，从而提高了模型在不确定性环境下的鲁棒性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "引入上下文感知的结构化先验，实现语义适应性模态融合。",
      "explanation": "VBF++设计了可学习的混合先验机制，根据视频的语义类别动态调整融合策略的先验分布，而非简单假设，使得模态权重分布能够自动聚类并与视频内容高度一致（例如动作片赋予视觉更高权重，音乐片赋予声学更高权重）。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过推荐引导的对抗性优化（RAR）对齐重构与推荐目标。",
      "explanation": "RAR 机制利用对抗训练，强制编码器生成的融合策略分布逼近推荐损失较低的高质量策略集合，有效解决了传统变分自编码器仅关注特征重构质量而忽略推荐排序准确性的目标错位问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "集成元学习器，有效解决推荐系统的冷启动和跨域适应性问题。",
      "explanation": "VBF++利用元学习（MAML 思想）快速调整模型参数，使其能迅速适应新内容和新领域，显著提升了模型在稀疏数据和跨域推荐场景下的泛化能力和性能。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "现有的主流方法面临着一个根本性的挑战：它们倾向于为给定的输入计算一个单一的、最优的权重向量，将多模态融合视为寻找'全局唯一最优解'的优化问题。",
    "VBF++ 的核心思想是将多模态融合过程重新表述为一个变分推理问题，成功将融合范式从传统的'点估计'转变为更具鲁棒性的'分布建模'范式。",
    "传统注意力机制结果几乎坍缩在空间中的同一个点，模型缺乏弹性，无法对融合权重的可信度进行建模。",
    "VBF++策略分布呈现出一个结构化的椭圆置信区域，围绕在高质量策略中心附近。这证明模型成功学习到了一个后验分布，在保留必要探索空间的同时，确保了准确性。",
    "VBF++ 成功地为多模态视频推荐系统引入了不确定性建模，实现了从确定性点估计到变分贝叶斯融合的范式转变。"
  ],
